# Book Recommendation Website

This plan details the creation of a stunning, modern book recommendation web application. The application will allow users to discover new books, search for specific titles or genres, and view detailed information about books. 

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The app will be built using React and Vite. I will create the project in a new folder at `C:\Users\NEVYA\.gemini\antigravity\scratch\book-recommender`.
> We will use the free Google Books API to fetch real book data (covers, titles, authors, descriptions) so the app is fully functional and has rich content right away.

## Open Questions

